b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":816,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Issue Regarding Locked Mercurial Gauntlet (Flame)","message":"<div>We have confirmed an issue where the The Mercurial Gauntlet (Flame) quest gets locked after moving to on of the locked High Dragon Trials Master quests.<\/div><div>This issue can be resolved by moving to a quest with no locked level of difficulty, as per the example below.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Assuming all levels of difficulty for Avenue to Power are unlocked:<\/div><div>1. Tap Events in the home screen.<\/div><div>2. Tap Avenue to Power.<\/div><div>3. Go back to the home screen and tap Events once more.<\/div><div>4. Tap The Mercurial Gauntlet. The Mercurial Gauntlet (Flame) will now be unlocked and playable once again.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We are currently investigating the cause of this issue.<\/div><div>Any further updates will be posted in this notice.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.&quot;<\/div>","start_time":1571109600,"prev_article_id":"811","next_article_id":"819","image_path":"","update_time":1571109595}}}'